From Alan Cooney Subject Re Membrane keypad with custom Try the folks at Dimolex La Crescenta CA Their number is They make membrane keypads that are very flat in layouts from to They have standard models tactile models with stainless domes under each key to make a 'click' you can feel as well as backlit Some of them can even be cut with scissors to form a funky shape other than a Many of the models are available in a 'kit' which includes a bezel colored and plain key covers and rub on lettering to make your own One piece prices aren't cheap though as they want for one four position pad kit and for a position kit I have no affiliation with Dimolex or any company connected with I have purchased a couple of keypads from them and am pleased with what I Cheers Alan